Method Detail

getCursor

public String getCursor()
A string that is used to keep track of your current state. On the next call to Dropbox.delta(java.lang.String), pass in this value to pick up where you left off.

isReset

public boolean isReset()
If true, then you should reset your local state to be an empty folder before processing the list of delta entries. This is only true in rare situations.

getEntries

public List<DeltaEntry> getEntries()
Apply these entries to your local state to catch up with the Dropbox server's state.

hasMore

public boolean hasMore()
If true, then there are more entries available; you can call Dropbox.delta(java.lang.String) again immediately to retrieve those entries. If false, then wait at least 5 minutes (preferably longer) before checking again.
